<td><strong>Google AI Overviews</strong></td>
<td>Links to 3+ sources per answer</td>
<td>E-E-A-T signals, structured content, pages with entities</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>ChatGPT (web search)</strong></td>
<td>Inline citations with source links</td>
<td>Recent content, authoritative domains, direct answers</td>
</tr>
